# HMError.Code.renameWithSimilarName

**Case**

An attempt to rename an object with its current name.

## Declaration

```swift
case renameWithSimilarName
```

## Collision errors

- **HMError.Code.homeWithSimilarNameExists**: An attempt to assign a home the same name as an existing home.
- **HMError.Code.objectWithSimilarNameExists**: An object with a similar name already exists.
- **HMError.Code.objectWithSimilarNameExistsInHome**: An attempt to give the name of one object to another object in the home.
